# - Fixed: Corrected all field paths in checks to match emit structure
# - Fixed: Added describe_cost_category_definition discovery for costexplorer_cost_data_exports_private_and_encrypted rule
# - Fixed: Corrected list_cost_category_definitions emit field paths
# - All checks executed successfully against AWS
# - 0 execution errors
# - Field paths verified correct
# - Tested: 2026-01-08
